## ✅ **`.dockerignore`**

```dockerignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
env/
venv/
.venv/
ENV/
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg
MANIFEST

# Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
ENV/
env/

# IDEs
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store

# Git
.git/
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# Docker
Dockerfile
docker-compose.yml
docker-compose.*.yml
.dockerignore

# CI/CD
.github/
.gitlab-ci.yml
.travis.yml

# Documentation
README.md
CHANGELOG.md
LICENSE
docs/

# Tests
tests/
test_*.py
*_test.py
pytest.ini
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/
*.cover

# Database files (don't include in image)
*.db
*.db-journal
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# Logs
*.log
logs/

# Environment files
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Alembic (migrations applied separately)
alembic.ini
alembic/

# Static files (if any)
static/
media/

# Temporary files
tmp/
temp/
*.tmp

# OS files
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store

# Node (if you have frontend)
node_modules/
npm-debug.log
yarn-error.log

# Jupyter notebooks
*.ipynb
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# ML models (too large)
*.pkl
*.h5
*.onnx
models/

# Backup files
*.bak
*.backup
*~

# Cache
.cache/
*.cache

# Misc
*.pid
*.seed
*.pid.lock
